data.description: Impressive 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath ranch style home in the ideal location between New Albany, Sunbury and Johnstown.  The spacious kitchen has a breakfast island plus additional dining area.  The living room with vaulted ceilings leads to the back deck perfect for grilling and chilling.   Primary suite has a private bath with shower, large jetted tub and walk-in closet.  2 additional bedrooms share the hallway bath.  Full basement offers plenty of additional space and storage.  2 car garage and over 1 acre of land for all your outdoor activities.
